OL,3,CWoman stole man's mobility scooter and
OL,4,Cleft him to die in -6C temperatures
OL,6,FA homeless drug addict who stole a
OL,7,Fvulnerable man's mobility scooter and
OL,8,Fleft him to die in freezing conditions
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for his manslaughter.
OL,11,FNeil Shadwick, 63, was dragged along a
OL,12,Froad by Kimberley Ann Hawkins, 41, as
OL,13,Fshe sped away from a Tesco supermarket
OL,14,Fin Stroud.
OL,16,FMr Shadwick had Parkinson's and
OL,17,Fstruggled with his mobility and
OL,18,Fcommunication. He was classed as
OL,19,Fvulnerable and had been exploited in
OL,20,Fthe past.
