OL,3,CWoman stole man's mobility scooter and
OL,4,Cleft him to die in -6C temperatures
OL,6,FIn the early hours of 22 January last
OL,7,Fyear, Hawkins and Mr Shadwick had gone
OL,8,Fto two cash machines to get money.
OL,10,FCCTV showed the father-of-two riding
OL,11,Fon his scooter to the Tesco cash
OL,12,Fmachine. Hawkins was sat on his lap.
OL,14,FBut when Mr Shadwick was unable to
OL,15,Fwithdraw cash, Hawkins stole his
OL,16,Fscooter and sped off - dragging him
OL,17,Falong for around 100m until he fell
OL,18,Foff.
