OL,3,CWoman stole man's mobility scooter and
OL,4,Cleft him to die in -6C temperatures
OL,6,FIt was around 1.45am, and temperatures
OL,7,Fhad plummetted to -6C. Mr Shadwick
OL,8,Fmanaged to drag himself back to the
OL,9,FATM to try to retrieve his bank card,
OL,10,Fbut then he collapsed.
OL,12,FHe was not found until 5.30am, when
OL,13,FTesco staff arrived to open the store.
OL,15,FDrifting in and out of consciousness,
OL,16,FMr Shadwick was able to tell them
OL,17,F"Kim" and "robbery" before he was
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital, where he died later
OL,19,Fthat day as a result of hypothermia.
