OL,3,CWoman stole man's mobility scooter and
OL,4,Cleft him to die in -6C temperatures
OL,6,FMr Shadwick's scooter was later found
OL,7,Fabandoned by a member of the public on
OL,8,FBisley Old Road.
OL,10,FHawkins previously pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fhis manslaughter, aggravated vehicle
OL,12,Ftaking and assault occasioning actual
OL,13,Fbodily harm.
OL,15,FDuring a hearing at Gloucester Crown
OL,16,FCourt on Thursday 29 August, she was
OL,17,Fsentenced to six year's in prison for
OL,18,Fher role in Mr Shadwick's death.
