OL,3,CWoman stole man's mobility scooter and
OL,4,Cleft him to die in -6C temperatures
OL,6,F"The defendant continues to move on
OL,7,Fwithout stopping and abandons the
OL,8,Fscooter on Bisley Old Road.
OL,10,F"The temperature that night was below
OL,11,Ffreezing, and it was sufficiently cold
OL,12,Ffor the local council to activate the
OL,13,Fsevere weather emergency protocol.
OL,15,F"Staff working at the Tesco that night
OL,16,Fdescribed it as freezing and said the
OL,17,Ftemperature was between -4C and -6C."
OL,19,FShe added: "She did what she did out
OL,20,Fof a fit of pique. It was selfish and
OL,21,Fspiteful but not premeditated."
