OL,6,FDetective Inpsector Adam Stacey, from
OL,7,FGloucestershire Police, described
OL,8,FHawkin's actions as "callous, vile and
OL,9,Fabsolutely disgusting".
OL,11,F"It is hard to imagine what goes
OL,12,Fthrough someone's mind at that point.
OL,13,FKimberley Hawkins' actions that night
OL,14,Fwere reprehensible."
